Content:: Elena Bodnarenco (5 March 1965 – 4 July 2022) was a Moldovan politician. A member of the Party of Communists of the Republic of Moldova, she served in the Parliament from 2005 to 2011, 2014 to 2019, and again from 2021 to 2022.[1] Bodnarenco died of cancer in Chișinău on 4 July 2022 at the age of 57.[2]  This article about a mayor in Moldova is a stub.
